  "transcript": {
    "language": "en",
    "is_generated": false,
    "segments": [
      {
        "start": 0.2,
        "duration": 0.9,
        "text": "- [David] Hello, wordsmiths."
      },
      {
        "start": 1.1,
        "duration": 2.0,
        "text": "Please put on this protective suit"
      },
      {
        "start": 3.1,
        "duration": 2.2,
        "text": "as you enter Khan Academy Labs."
      },
      {
        "start": 5.4,
        "duration": 1.6,
        "text": "Over here in V Branch,"
      },
      {
        "start": 7.0,
        "duration": 2.8,
        "text": "we're working on our\nvocabulary accelerator,"
      },
      {
        "start": 9.8,
        "duration": 3.7,
        "text": "smashing together word parts\nto make brand new words."
      },
      {
        "start": 16.6,
        "duration": 1.3,
        "text": "Here comes one now."
      },
      {
        "start": 17.9,
        "duration": 1.4,
        "text": "Megalithogram."
      },
      {
        "start": 19.3,
        "duration": 3.8,
        "text": "It's a message written on a very big rock,"
      },
      {
        "start": 23.1,
        "duration": 1.7,
        "text": "very big rock writing."
      },
      {
        "start": 24.8,
        "duration": 1.9,
        "text": "Now, today we're going\nto go with some older,"
      },
      {
        "start": 26.7,
        "duration": 1.6,
        "text": "more stable words."
      },
      {
        "start": 28.3,
        "duration": 0.8,
        "text": "I'll define them."
      },
      {
        "start": 29.1,
        "duration": 1.3,
        "text": "We'll look at some related words,"
      },
      {
        "start": 30.4,
        "duration": 2.8,
        "text": "and then we'll use each one in a sentence."
      },
      {
        "start": 33.2,
        "duration": 0.9,
        "text": "So let's get to it."
      },
      {
        "start": 34.1,
        "duration": 4.4,
        "text": "The words are hypothesis,\ndemonstrate, and accurate."
      },
      {
        "start": 38.5,
        "duration": 1.7,
        "text": "A hypothesis is a noun,"
      },
      {
        "start": 40.2,
        "duration": 1.9,
        "text": "and it's a theory or explanation"
      },
      {
        "start": 42.1,
        "duration": 1.7,
        "text": "that hasn't been proved yet."
      },
      {
        "start": 43.9,
        "duration": 2.4,
        "text": "In science, you start\nout with a hypothesis"
      },
      {
        "start": 46.3,
        "duration": 3.2,
        "text": "and then you set about trying\nto see if it's right or wrong."
      },
      {
        "start": 50.5,
        "duration": 1.6,
        "text": "Demonstrate is a verb,"
      },
      {
        "start": 52.1,
        "duration": 3.6,
        "text": "and it means to show how\nsomething is done or used."
      },
      {
        "start": 55.7,
        "duration": 1.9,
        "text": "Accurate is an adjective"
      },
      {
        "start": 57.6,
        "duration": 2.8,
        "text": "and it means true, correct, or exact."
      },
      {
        "start": 60.4,
        "duration": 2.9,
        "text": "The noun form accuracy is the state"
      },
      {
        "start": 63.3,
        "duration": 3.0,
        "text": "of being true, correct, or exact."
      },
      {
        "start": 66.3,
        "duration": 1.4,
        "text": "Now, word origins."
      },
      {
        "start": 68.6,
        "duration": 3.4,
        "text": "Hypothesis comes from the\nGreek hypo, meaning below,"
      },
      {
        "start": 72.1,
        "duration": 2.7,
        "text": "and thes, meaning to put or place."
      },
      {
        "start": 74.8,
        "duration": 2.7,
        "text": "A hypothesis is placed\nbeneath the argument"
      },
      {
        "start": 77.5,
        "duration": 0.9,
        "text": "you're trying to make."
      },
      {
        "start": 78.4,
        "duration": 1.9,
        "text": "It's the basis or the foundation."
      },
      {
        "start": 80.2,
        "duration": 1.8,
        "text": "In science, it's your premise."
      },
      {
        "start": 82.0,
        "duration": 3.7,
        "text": "Without the hypothesis,\nthe whole idea falls apart."
      },
      {
        "start": 85.7,
        "duration": 1.8,
        "text": "Hypo is a prefix you'll find"
      },
      {
        "start": 87.5,
        "duration": 3.2,
        "text": "in all sorts of science\nterms like hypothermia,"
      },
      {
        "start": 90.7,
